https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5iClIlKzr8qDi61NQB5e0uq6v6p.jpg Cindy, the doll is mine is a short film by French director Bertrand Bonello. It stars Italian actress Asia Argento in the double role of photographer Cindy Sherman, a brunette, and her model, a blonde who strangely resemble one another. The film was screened out of competition at the 2005 Cannes Film Festival. Cindy, the Doll Is Mine
